US Army Major General Austin S. Miller is the commander of the US Joint Special Operations Command, which directs all US special-forces operations worldwide.

SEa, Air and Land, the Navy's primary special operations force and a component of the Naval Special Warfare Command.

The deck crew of an aircraft carrier are responsible for launching and recovering aircraft. Each crew member wears a colored jersey to distinguish his function.
